00:12:54.274 --> 00:12:55.981
moet efficiÃ«nter worden,

00:12:56.005 --> 00:12:57.731
en ze moet diverser worden.

00:12:57.741 --> 00:12:59.154
Het juiste spul

00:12:59.154 --> 00:13:01.598
